docs/handoff/CURRENT_HANDOFF.md:125:Relevant terminal blocks must end with the mandatory final SUMMARY block. Use `NEXT_CHAT_REPLY: p` only when `OVERALL RESULT: PASS` and `REMOTE_EVIDENCE: PASS`. Use `NEXT_CHAT_REPLY: f` when the work failed but remote evidence is available. Use `NEXT_CHAT_REPLY: paste-output` when remote evidence is missing or incomplete.
