docs/reports/terminal/20260519-211235_20260519-final-summary-runner-inspection.log:51:docs/handoff/CURRENT_HANDOFF.md:64:Relevant terminal blocks must end with the mandatory final SUMMARY block. Use `NEXT_CHAT_REPLY: p` only when `OVERALL RESULT: PASS` and `REMOTE_EVIDENCE: PASS`. Use `NEXT_CHAT_REPLY: f` when the work failed but remote evidence is available. Use `NEXT_CHAT_REPLY: paste-output` when remote evidence is missing or incomplete.
docs/reports/terminal/20260519-211235_20260519-final-summary-runner-inspection.log:52:docs/handoff/CURRENT_HANDOFF.md:89:- Final summary contract: relevant workflow blocks must end with the framed SUMMARY contract containing WORK RESULT, EVIDENCE RESULT, OVERALL RESULT, REMOTE_EVIDENCE, terminal_log, command_report, NEXT_CHAT_REPLY, and final result marker.
