docs/reports/terminal/v0.3.36_standard_error_contract_prep.log:3764:docs/STATUS.md:165:The no-copy/evidence workflow now requires a mandatory final SUMMARY block for relevant terminal work. `WORK RESULT`, `EVIDENCE RESULT`, `OVERALL RESULT`, `REMOTE_EVIDENCE`, `terminal_log`, `command_report`, and `NEXT_CHAT_REPLY` must be reported separately. A final PASS requires work success and evidence success; a pushed log can prove a failure without turning that failure into success.
